Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:05.72,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,Wait, Yuta. Tuck in your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:08.01,Default,Futokazu,0,0,0,,I'm off. I'll be home \Ntoday around 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:09.82,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,Okay, have a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.49,0:00:51.73,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:52.67,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,Were you here long?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:54.10,Default,M,0,0,0,,Not long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:56.09,Default,M,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:31.00,Bengoshi-Kodera,Plaque,0,0,0,,Kodera
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:34.19,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:39.45,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.65,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Is the bath heated?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:41.54,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:44.09,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,You got home from work early.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:47.47,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Yeah, and your job must've run late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:49.53,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,It's the end of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:53.33,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I've been running around\N to meet my quota.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:55.76,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,My hips can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:23.67,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Mix it thoroughly and then \Nspread it on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:28.51,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei, I didn't come to work \Nhere to do stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:31.44,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,After that, put this on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:33.10,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.13,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.04,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Seaweed boiled in soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.81,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Seaweed boiled in soy sauce...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:41.83,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's just a theory of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:45.78,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,but side dishes that go well with rice \Nusually go well with bread, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.68,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,This should only be eaten with rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:52.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,This bread is topped with pickled\N daikon radish slices.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:55.77,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,That should be eaten with rice, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.66,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,Office Landlord:\N Toyama Yoshie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.66,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You've got a lot free time, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.25,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Oh, Yoshie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.45,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please try my pickled bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.37,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.67,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,I'm hungry, but not that hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:11.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's unexpectedly good, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:14.69,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,The word "unexpectedly" \Ndoes not inspire confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.72,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,How are you going to make\N the monthly rent like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'll have last month's for you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:22.29,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,By the way, it's actually \Nthe month before last's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:24.30,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,What made you think you \Ndidn't owe that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.45,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Is there work coming to this office?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:30.02,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Attorney: \NHakamada Yukio
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:28.80,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:31.79,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We have a number of ongoing clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.79,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Right, Shinozuka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.50,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,Yes. One client.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.50,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)}Temp:\N Shinozuka Rina
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:41.61,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You've only got one, \Nso don't exaggerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.20,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Hey, Kanae-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.77,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)}Hakamada's Assistant: \NNonomura Kanae
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:43.66,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.77,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You're gathering material for your
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:48.44,Bengoshi-Top,Yoshie,0,0,0,,lawyer manga while you \Nwork at this office, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:49.71,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:52.63,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Can't you use the manga \Nto advertise the firm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:55.51,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I don't have that kind \Nof authorization yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:59.02,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I have syndication, but I'm \Nstill treated like a newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:00.85,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,How useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.76,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Seriously useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.13,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.14,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.96,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Oh. Kodera-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:12.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.18,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:18.41,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,That's the ongoing client \Nhe mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:21.89,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Her husband's cheating on her, \Nand she's considering compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:24.83,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I see. She's pretty, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:29.14,Bengoshi-Top,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I captured my husband \Nhaving an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.88,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,Client of this episode: \NKodera Kiyomi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:32.19,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.52,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,And thank you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:41.19,Bengoshi-Spy_Marilyn,DVD box-set,0,0,0,,Iron Spy Woman \N{\fs25\c&HCED4DD&}Marilyn
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.19,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,It had useful information, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:45.16,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(390,390)}Private Investigator:\N Umemoto Kurumi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.86,Bengoshi-Top,Kurumi,0,0,0,,If you need to know the rest of the \Nstory, I'll let you borrow more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:48.96,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I have all 108 episodes, \Nup to season 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.21,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:57.23,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,This should be ample evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.93,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,In all honesty, it's \Nincomprehensible to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:03.05,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Why would my husband be \Nattracted to a woman like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.09,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,Excuse me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.54,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You're right. She's plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.65,Default,Yoshie,0,0,0,,You're way prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.22,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,How typical.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:16.43,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,The partner in infidelity is usually \Nless attractive than the wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.74,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Men have low standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:20.13,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Especially men like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:24.44,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I also have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.44,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I took this in front of \Nthat woman's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.80,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.44,Default,Yoshie & Kurumi,0,0,0,,Double adultery!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:36.52,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,She's married, and she has a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:41.62,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,They look like a happy family\N from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.84,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,She should be happy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.86,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Why would she cheat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:51.17,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Speaking as a woman,\N I can't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:56.00,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I cannot forgive this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.71,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.69,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Kiyomi-san, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:07.91,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Compensation can be collected \Nfrom the mistress, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.09,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:21.77,Bengoshi-Title,,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser\N{\fs25}~Let's Turn Your Tears into Money~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:26.97,Bengoshi-Ep_Title,Caption left,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser Episode 2 \NDouble Adultery! A Grueling Court Battle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.50,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,Sorry. Were you here long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.50,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.40,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,You can be late tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:36.51,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,Yeah. I told him there's a mother's \Nmeeting at the elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:40.25,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,My wife said she'd be late, too. \NWe can take our time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.87,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I represent Kodera Kiyomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.21,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,My name is Hakamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:50.46,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm his assistant, Nonomura Kanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:54.16,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption left,0,0,0,,{\a3}{\fad(380,0)}Kiyomi's husband\N Kodera Fumiya
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:54.16,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption right,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)}Fumiya's lover\N Togawa Yuko
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:54.16,Bengoshi-Top,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Kiyomi's representative?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:57.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'd like the two of \Nyou to see something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.69,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:12.29,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,They were taken last Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.75,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Both of you have spouses, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.72,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,you seem to be intimate \Nwith one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.06,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,As a representative, \Nlet me ask you directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:28.26,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Were the two of you having \Nan illicit affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You're at a loss for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'll ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.55,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The two of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.16,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Were you doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.58,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.94,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We have a lot evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.62,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I think you might as well own up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.17,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.82,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That's judicious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:04.66,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,No, we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.63,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.70,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,We're not having an illicit affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:10.77,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,No, no, no matter how you look \Nat it, you went to a hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.30,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,I never went in any hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:15.51,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,We just had lunch at a place \Nin front of this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.47,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,This is a hotel district.\NWhy would you have lunch—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.72,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,He and I have been friends \Nsince high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:23.52,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,We discussed our family life. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:30.02,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,If you don't admit it, \Nthis will go to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.62,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,We don't want to go to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.96,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.14,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.95,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It will take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And attorney fees will \Nbe nothing to sneeze at.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:49.54,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,I don't need an attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.32,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Office_Sign,Letters,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:00.32,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,A trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.15,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:05.24,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,She won't admit to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:07.26,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,There's no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:12.80,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Actually, I've been \Nstruggling with something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:17.17,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's right for me to be\N compensated by the mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:23.68,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I think it would hurt her \Ninnocent child and husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.15,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.14,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I will go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.69,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:34.65,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Based on what you've told me,\N I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.92,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I'll fight it out in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:39.42,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,But, if it goes to court,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:41.70,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,won't that lessen the compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:45.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Well... in most cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:49.32,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Then, we should bill the husband for \Ncompensation. He confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:52.05,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,But she's the kind of woman \Nwho lies and says she isn't cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:55.07,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I won't be satisfied \Nuntil I crush her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.98,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Let's calm down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:59.30,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.72,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.74,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'll make preparations for the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.18,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:06.52,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:14.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Going forward, there's someone \Nyou must have on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.10,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Kiyomi. I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.68,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,You admit you cheated, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:26.58,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Yeah. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.44,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.85,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,How long has it been going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.36,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Since the class reunion last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.17,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.17,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,We were both in drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:48.10,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,We were just club mates at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:55.85,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,But, at the reunion, she said \Nshe liked me and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.87,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.48,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I'm really stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:03.96,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Stupid! I'm stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.16,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Don't torture yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:12.35,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I understand your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.15,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:18.94,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,You always hear about affairs \Nthat start at class reunions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.24,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:25.71,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.84,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.57,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:34.61,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Why must the husband be on her side?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.85,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,He's a major culprit, a cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:40.32,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Our opponent this time \Nis quite a conundrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:44.93,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,In order for the court to accept \Nthe fact of the adultery,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:47.48,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,we need sound evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:53.26,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Thus, it would be faster to question \Nthe culprit of the illicit affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:57.47,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It would be more \Nconvincing and real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:02.38,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,She's a housewife, so usually \Nwe'd meet at noon on a workday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:05.97,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,It was convenient because I have to \Nmake my rounds out of the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:06.93,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.66,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Most of the time, we went \Nto love hotels in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.88,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,They have places that give\N discounts during workdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.28,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,What days are those, specifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.26,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.14,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.26,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I have a points card.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:26.96,Bengoshi-Hotel_Charlotte,Point Card,0,0,0,,Hotel \NCharlotte
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:29.89,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,So many...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.89,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Yeah. I have another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:42.94,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Sorry. That was insensitive of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.01,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,No, you're helping me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:46.68,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.26,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:52.41,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,There was a time their rooms were full.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:54.69,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,It was only once, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.02,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,In that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:58.17,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.84,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,But it was only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.53,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:07.87,Bengoshi-Anger,Repeated word,0,0,0,,Anger Anger Anger
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:08.73,Bengoshi-Anger,Repeated word,0,0,0,,Anger Anger Anger
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.00,Bengoshi-Anger,Repeated word,0,0,0,,{\fs30\b1}Anger Anger Anger
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.17,Bengoshi-Statement,Letter title,0,0,0,,Statement
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.21,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,They even did it in your home...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.91,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Hearing it made me nauseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:20.18,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I had no idea he was \Nthat insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.70,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He's desperate to get \Nhimself out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:26.42,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Well, that's to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.19,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Think of it this way:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:30.46,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Every word he speaks will turn into money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:33.04,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:37.05,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I will make preparations for the \Nhearing based on this statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:40.01,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,My husband says he'll go to court, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:42.51,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,He said he'll bear witness, \Nand do anything I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:45.14,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Tell him you don't want him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:46.16,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:49.30,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It happens often. The party in \Nquestion takes the stand,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:53.01,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,has an emotional outburst, \Nand hurts the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:56.62,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'm worried that's what \Nyour husband might do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.15,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:03.20,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Aside from that, to have the \Nupper hand in the hearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.90,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,there are two things I need \N you to drag out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.06,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:11.83,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,First, you have to make \Nhim say, "I did wrong."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:18.50,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That will make it clear that Fumiya-san \Nand Yuko-san had an illicit affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.41,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,How is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:23.36,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Sexless or infertile marriages
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:26.80,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,can be seen as an existing break\N between husband and wife
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.04,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and make it more difficult \Nto receive compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.61,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We have to eliminate \Nall those arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:33.62,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:37.84,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,And the other thing which you have\N to drag out of your husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:42.93,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,He has to say, "My partner \Nwas the instigator."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:46.37,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I truly did wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:49.50,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,So you feel you've done wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:53.30,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Yeah. I absolutely did wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:57.37,Bengoshi-Did_Wrong,Words on monitor,0,0,0,,I absolutely did wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:59.52,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,You've always been supportive of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:02.97,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,When things weren't \Ngoing well at my work,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:05.42,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,you worked at home and \Nhelped our finances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.00,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,When I got in the scooter accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.76,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,you nursed me and never left my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.24,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I am truly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:14.46,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I'm your wife, it's only normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:16.52,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:22.24,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,You and I haven't talked\Nlike this in so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:26.23,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I feel like we're newlyweds again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:27.62,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:31.61,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,One final thing I'd like to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:34.28,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Did you instigate the affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.31,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:36.75,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Well, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.05,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:41.22,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,No, she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:45.40,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Yuko's the one who suggested we \Ngo to a hotel after the reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:48.93,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I think she said, "let's get \Ntogether" more times than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:50.36,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:52.83,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,So, she instigated the affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:55.77,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,That's right. She was the instigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:58.36,Bengoshi-Instigator,Monitor,0,0,0,,She was the instigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.03,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.76,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I think I've told you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.61,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I'm glad you recollected everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.38,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:10.64,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I did it for you. Of course I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.92,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Something went wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:16.98,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.09,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:23.38,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Anyway, please sign here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:24.68,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:32.85,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Isn't the husband saying, "she was\N the instigator" his subjective opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:34.05,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.22,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It doesn't carry as much \Nweight as evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:37.34,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What's the point, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:39.08,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.50,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Look forward to the hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.59,Bengoshi-Court,Plaque,0,0,0,,Court of Law
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:52.36,Bengoshi-Oral_Proceedings,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)}The first oral proceedings
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:56.59,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I didn't think a case like this \Nwould be held at district court.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:58.56,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Where did you think it would be held?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:01.79,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Since it's a domestic case, I thought it \Nwould be at the domestic relations court.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:05.96,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,A compensatory action between a married \Ncouple can be held at domestic relations court,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:13.21,Bengoshi-Vocab_Word,Caption on upper right,0,0,0,,{\fad(540,540)}Compensatory Lawsuit
