Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:25.25,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,in room 502 of the Hotel Charlotte,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:29.33,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,at which time they had their \Nsecond sexual encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:33.55,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Lastly, to repeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:40.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,every rendezvous they had was \Ninstigated by the defendant,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:45.41,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,as Fumiya-san has stated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.48,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.29,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,She's quite worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.27,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Wow, you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:04.18,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.87,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.30,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,I never seduced him, not once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:19.35,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,Fumiya-san seduced me every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.11,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:22.88,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:24.78,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,I was forced to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:27.99,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,And he raped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:28.91,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:29.69,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,...pe?
