Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:35.13,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please stay calm, Kiyomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:39.63,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,So, you were raped, and the \Nrelationship was one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:40.58,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:42.67,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:52.18,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:55.06,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Why didn't you make a counterargument?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:59.69,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Actually, it was lucky \NYuko-san made that remark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:00.59,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:06.43,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's not Yuko-san who we're\N fighting. It's the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.89,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.00,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Who is lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:15.01,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Who's statement should be believed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:16.78,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's her word against ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.07,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Statements made in angry outbursts
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.94,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,make the judge suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:26.13,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,So, in order to drag that out of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:28.28,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,you purposefully made her mad by
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:32.78,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,revealing Fumiya-san's statement \Nabout her being the aggressor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.50,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:41.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please inform Fumiya-san \Nabout what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:46.20,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I raped her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.57,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.57,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Does this look like she's being forced?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:04.19,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:08.57,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,So, Yuko-san is lying, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:11.48,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Of course it's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:14.23,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Yuko was the lead in this play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:17.23,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,This cosplay was Yuko's idea, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.99,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Memories of our drama club \Ndays came back to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.40,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,and we got crazy hot with \Neach other that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.50,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Man, I'm mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.93,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I'm fighting back with all I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:30.18,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I'll give you whatever evidence you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:34.00,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,She has to pay for her offense, \Nthrough and through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.37,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:43.56,Bengoshi-Love_Hotel_Photos,Words on top,0,0,0,,Love hotel photos
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:47.89,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,These photos were taken on \NJune 8th at the Hotel Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.82,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It is clear that they \Nwent to the hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:53.90,Bengoshi-Oral_Proceedings3,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(520,520)}The third oral proceedings
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.61,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and then she dressed up in\N a high school uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:57.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and thereby engaged in illicit actions
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,by her own volition.
