Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:20.19,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,Please elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:25.49,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,After he raped me, he took \Nthose pictures of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.32,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,He said if I refused to see him again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:32.71,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,he would show the photos to my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:38.00,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,That is why I met with \NFumiya-san repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.12,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,That school uniform was also his idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:46.24,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:50.11,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The more stories she tells, \Nthe greater our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:52.76,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,After all, she has no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.39,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,I have proof.
