Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:00.33,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,She does?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:07.46,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,The audio recording I have here \Nis proof that he threatened me.
