Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:55.50,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,It was because I was taken by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:02.13,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,He began making threats like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:05.34,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,and he made me\Nmeet him many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:12.82,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,But, I never did it with \NFumiya-san willingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.26,0:23:21.58,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,I was desperate to protect my family.
