Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.62,0:28:01.02,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Come on. Se—
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.13,0:28:03.04,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,"Se"...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.67,0:28:05.00,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,You're so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.00,0:28:06.60,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,What time do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.60,0:28:08.22,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Umemoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.52,0:28:10.82,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,What are you doing here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.82,0:28:12.42,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I got so bored,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.42,0:28:15.45,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,I started watching the forbidden fifth season.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.20,0:28:17.24,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.47,0:28:22.18,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,"Iron Spy Woman Marilyn,"\N the greatest series in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.18,0:28:24.65,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Watch one episode and \Nyou're hooked to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.65,0:28:26.57,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,It's the forbidden fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.57,0:28:27.71,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.71,0:28:29.65,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,We're in a crisis here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.65,0:28:32.53,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,I'll take a rain check \Non that cherry pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.02,0:28:36.40,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Oh. Can you make us some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.07,0:28:39.32,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.50,0:28:44.50,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,But same to you, Sensei. \NWhy are you here so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.01,0:28:47.94,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I was examining the audio recording evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.94,0:28:51.78,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. That's the creepy \None I've been hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.52,0:28:55.57,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,In this drama-freak's opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.57,0:28:57.32,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,it's a bad script.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.13,0:29:00.59,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's not scripted.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.59,0:29:02.76,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The situation was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.76,0:29:04.18,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.18,0:29:06.19,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,It's obvious they're reading lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.19,0:29:08.96,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,The guy actor especially.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.04,0:29:11.70,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Does it sound that way to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.77,0:29:17.71,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,A high school drama club \Ncould do it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.12,0:29:21.50,Default,Kurumi,0,0,0,,Drama club...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.69,0:29:31.04,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.04,0:29:32.48,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Oh, Kiyomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.48,0:29:33.56,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.56,0:29:34.79,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Is Hakamada-sensei here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.79,0:29:36.08,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,He's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.08,0:29:37.68,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'll call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.65,0:29:42.97,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Hello, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.97,0:29:44.50,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.90,0:29:46.42,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I'm doing a little research.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.87,0:29:50.15,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Kodera Kiyomi-san is at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.72,0:29:54.22,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.80,0:29:57.71,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I asked my husband about the threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.89,0:30:00.01,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.01,0:30:02.99,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,He said he never made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.99,0:30:06.13,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,May I have a copy of \Nthe audio recording, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.13,0:30:08.03,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I'm going to let my husband hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.03,0:30:09.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.86,0:30:10.61,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.61,0:30:15.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,There are some things I need to \Nascertain before the next hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.43,0:30:20.87,Bengoshi-Court,Plaque,0,0,0,,Court of Law
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.53,0:30:21.23,Bengoshi-Oral_Proceedings,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)}The fourth oral proceedings
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.57,0:30:24.70,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,This is the threatening \Nemail Fumiya-san sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.27,0:30:30.42,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,In 3,000 words he states \Nthat he'll destroy my family
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.42,0:30:32.75,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,if I don't continue seeing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.12,0:30:39.27,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.68,0:30:41.11,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.63,0:30:46.99,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Are you sure this email \Nwas sent by Fumiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.99,0:30:50.70,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,The sender's email is Fumiya-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.38,0:30:52.76,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.37,0:30:54.83,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.38,0:31:01.67,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.67,0:31:04.17,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yes. It's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.66,0:31:15.94,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Your Honor, if I may?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.94,0:31:17.48,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.40,0:31:27.31,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Can we replay the audio recording which \Nhas been presented to the court?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.95,0:31:34.23,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.23,0:31:37.04,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Yuko,0,0,0,,I don't want to. This is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.63,0:31:39.52,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Refuse all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.52,0:31:42.46,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Fumiya,0,0,0,,But what would your husband \Nsay if he saw these pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.46,0:31:44.29,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Yuko,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.29,0:31:47.35,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I can hand the photos out \Nto your neighbors, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.35,0:31:49.05,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Yuko,0,0,0,,Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.49,0:31:52.18,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Then get on your knees like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.18,0:31:54.63,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Come on. Se—
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.05,0:31:59.24,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Upon examination of the audio recording,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.98,0:32:06.51,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,there was no sign of \Nfabrication or editing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.93,0:32:12.23,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Clearly, the voices are those \Nof Fumiya-san and Yuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.95,0:32:16.10,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,However, there is \Nsomething dubious about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.85,0:32:18.88,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Therefore, to clear my doubts,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.35,0:32:21.98,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I ask for the defendant's cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.52,0:32:23.35,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.57,0:32:32.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please read from this script.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.45,0:32:35.23,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.62,0:32:42.97,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.92,0:32:46.92,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.59,0:32:50.38,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,I don't want to. This is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.38,0:32:52.81,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Could you read it with more emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.39,0:32:58.62,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You were active in high school \Ndrama club, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.56,0:33:01.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.73,0:33:03.58,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Think of this place as the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.17,0:33:06.39,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.17,0:33:09.74,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.49,0:33:15.14,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,I don't want to. This is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.62,0:33:17.27,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Refuse all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.27,0:33:21.34,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But what would your husband \Nsay if he saw these photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.85,0:33:23.43,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.43,0:33:27.20,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I can hand the photos out \Nto your neighbors, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.51,0:33:29.39,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,Please, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.39,0:33:32.35,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,All right, then get on \Nyour knees like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.35,0:33:34.26,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Come on. Se—
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.89,0:33:38.85,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,All right, then get on \Nyour knees like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.85,0:33:40.76,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Come on. Se—
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.91,0:33:44.43,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,...n-s-e-i.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.31,0:33:46.53,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.53,0:33:48.57,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,"Sensei"?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.24,0:33:51.97,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Oh, happy day,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.97,0:33:57.65,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,for the pompous sensei \Nto show his true colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.75,0:34:01.22,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.62,0:34:04.37,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I got carried away with the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.42,0:34:12.09,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,This in fact is a script from \Na high school drama club
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.09,0:34:15.16,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Fumiya-san and Yuko-san were in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.09,0:34:15.16,Bengoshi-After_School,Script title,0,0,0,,After School Humiliation
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.25,0:34:19.73,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I borrowed it from \NYuko-san's alma mater.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.13,0:34:22.56,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's an erotic comedy tour de force,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.56,0:34:27.71,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,in which high school students take \Nrevenge on a spartan female teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.71,0:34:32.10,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Quite a provocative scenario \Nfor a high school drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.28,0:34:36.45,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The dubious aspect is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.32,0:34:40.89,Bengoshi-Script,Script,0,0,0,,Kazuya: "Come on, let's get started" \NYukie: "I don't want to, this is wrong."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.74,0:34:40.89,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The audio recording presented as \Nevidence and the script...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.89,0:34:43.06,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,are absolutely identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.43,0:34:48.80,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yuko-san and Fumiya-san were \Nhigh school classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.38,0:34:51.81,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,They were also in the drama club together.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.21,0:34:55.21,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,According to Fumiya-san's statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.21,0:35:00.87,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,conjuring their past \Nwould make them hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.27,0:35:03.62,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Memories of our drama class \Ndays came back to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.62,0:35:06.18,Bengoshi-Internal/Narrator,Fumiya,0,0,0,,and we got crazy hot with \Neach other that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.53,0:35:11.61,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The two of you had the script on hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.61,0:35:14.19,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,and while recalling fond memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.19,0:35:17.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,the two of you reenacted \Nthe play, thus the audio.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.49,0:35:21.50,Default,Yuko,0,0,0,,That's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.50,0:35:22.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Listen, Yuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.86,0:35:26.62,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The audio recording and the \Nthreatening email
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.92,0:35:31.32,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,can easily be proven false.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.69,0:35:40.26,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,By the way, you will \Nbe penalized for fraud,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.81,0:35:45.88,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,for having fabricated evidence \Nto avoid a monetary lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.62,0:35:53.02,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You'd be digging your own grave
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.45,0:35:56.86,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,if you were to persist any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.56,0:36:05.29,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,We rest our case.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.65,0:36:19.49,Bengoshi-Court,Plaque,0,0,0,,Court of Law
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.79,0:36:23.86,Bengoshi-Oral_Proceedings,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)}Judgment day
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.03,0:36:21.33,Default,Bailiff,0,0,0,,All rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.59,0:36:24.88,Default,Bailiff,0,0,0,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.37,0:36:30.73,Default,Bailiff,0,0,0,,Be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.78,0:36:38.06,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,I will now render my verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.12,0:36:46.01,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,The court has decided that there\N was indeed an illicit affair
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.39,0:36:57.49,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,between defendant, Togawa Yuko, and \N plaintiff's husband, Kodeara Fumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.18,0:37:11.70,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,Hence, the defendant is ordered to \Npay two million yen to the plaintiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.71,0:37:15.11,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.11,0:37:16.34,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,You won, Kiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.78,0:37:27.58,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.58,0:37:30.91,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything \Nyou've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.91,0:37:32.10,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.10,0:37:34.63,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You're the one had had to endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.59,0:37:39.63,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,For now, I'm relieved about \Nthe judge's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.35,0:37:42.46,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,I didn't know what was going to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.46,0:37:44.50,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,when she brought up the threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.50,0:37:47.47,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I wasn't worried at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.51,0:37:54.32,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's more difficult to prove that \Nan adulterous affair did not happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.96,0:37:58.12,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The compensation fee \Nmight have been less,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.51,0:38:01.66,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,had she confessed to it from the outset.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.66,0:38:03.39,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.18,0:38:06.64,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,If there was even a little confession,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.22,0:38:11.15,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,the court might show mercy \Nand decrease the amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.13,0:38:16.54,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But Yuko-san destroyed\N that chance, all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.44,0:38:20.67,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Good job, Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.67,0:38:21.85,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.85,0:38:23.41,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.92,0:38:26.66,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Did you see the look on Yuko's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.66,0:38:28.48,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,It made me feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.96,0:38:32.02,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,But you only get two million \Nfor all that work, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.68,0:38:34.98,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,You deserve more, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.49,0:38:38.11,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.65,0:38:43.05,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Kiyomi-san is due for more compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.05,0:38:44.56,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.56,0:38:46.40,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,How does that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.79,0:38:49.42,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I'm glad I cooperated.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.42,0:38:52.94,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I'm glad you had such a \Nfine attorney on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.94,0:38:54.45,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.90,0:38:55.81,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.81,0:38:56.89,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.25,0:39:00.37,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Divorce agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.08,0:39:01.05,Bengoshi-Divorce_Agreement,Words,0,0,0,,Divorce Agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.05,0:39:02.78,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I am divorcing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.78,0:39:04.18,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.52,0:39:09.85,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.42,0:39:12.74,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I was going to divorce \Nyou from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.40,0:39:15.03,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,So, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.37,0:39:19.00,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Will you compensate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.00,0:39:20.27,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Compensate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.27,0:39:21.66,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.66,0:39:23.37,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,I cooperated with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.37,0:39:25.24,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Were you tricking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.24,0:39:27.21,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,The nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.21,0:39:29.31,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,After all your cheating,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.31,0:39:33.48,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,after all blaming \Nit all on the mistress,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.48,0:39:36.92,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,after all the boasting you did \Nabout the steamy details...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.92,0:39:39.42,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Did you think we could go \Nback to the way we were?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.07,0:39:52.03,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Here's the statement proving all \Nof your adulterous activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.03,0:39:53.17,Bengoshi-Divorce_Agreement,Letter,0,0,0,,{\3c&H949BA8&}Statement
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.03,0:39:54.67,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,When the affair started.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.67,0:40:00.64,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,The number of times of \Nphysical relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.14,0:40:06.08,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,You even stamped and signed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.91,0:40:13.50,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Not even a fine attorney of my \Ncaliber could counter this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.81,0:40:23.55,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Computing the compensation fee, \Nit comes out to three million.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.99,0:40:25.93,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,That's about the size of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.16,0:40:27.95,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Three million?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.20,0:40:30.54,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,This is a joke, right, Kiyomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.90,0:40:32.97,Default,Fumiya,0,0,0,,Have mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.80,0:40:36.45,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Wasn't it you who said that an offender
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.08,0:40:42.65,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,should pay for it, \Nthrough and through?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.12,0:40:50.16,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,By the way, you can \Npay it in installments.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.50,0:41:06.76,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Sensei, you were always going to make \Nthe husband pay, too, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.62,0:41:10.51,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's the law, that if the \Nentire sum of the compensation
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.51,0:41:15.12,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,were taken from the \Nspouse's illicit partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.12,0:41:18.04,Default,Hakamada,0,0,0,,we cannot sue the other party.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.04,0:41:21.36,Default,Kanae,0,0,0,,Then how were you able \Nto sue Fumiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.00,0:41:29.72,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,If there is a divorce, then \Ncompensation is higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.09,0:41:31.33,Bengoshi-Vocab_Word2,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)}Compensation for illicit affairs
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.09,0:41:31.33,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition2,Caption2,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)}Compensation is higher when there is a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.23,0:41:34.09,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I presented the case to \Nthe court on the premise
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.09,0:41:38.00,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,that the couple are \Nnot getting a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.00,0:41:44.60,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,So I was able to sue Fumiya-san \Nfor the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.41,0:41:47.11,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition2,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)\c&HA72831&\b1}3 million yen{\c&HC0BEC4&\b0} (compensation fee) -{\c&HAC1F21&\b1} 2 million yen{\b0}{\c&HF3F2F7&} (Yuko's suit) = {\c&H1C04A1&\3c&HB4B6F7&\b0}1 million yen{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.41,0:41:47.11,Bengoshi-Vocab_Word2,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)}Lawsuit to husband Fumiya
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.32,0:41:48.61,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,I hope Kiyomi-san was satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.61,0:41:52.45,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,She got compensation from her \Nobnoxious husband and partner both.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.56,0:41:57.29,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.75,0:41:59.63,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.93,0:42:06.11,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,At least we got what we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.14,0:42:10.53,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,Um, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.98,0:42:12.04,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.47,0:42:17.84,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,Why are you a divorce lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.57,0:42:24.28,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Oh, the bread's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.76,0:42:31.48,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's pickles bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.48,0:42:33.29,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Try it fresh from the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.29,0:42:35.71,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.71,0:42:37.12,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But, you haven't had lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.12,0:42:38.72,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.72,0:42:40.72,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,This one turned out especially good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.72,0:42:41.77,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,Really, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.77,0:42:42.94,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,But, you should accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.94,0:42:44.01,Bengoshi-Top,Kanae,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.48,0:42:46.11,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.11,0:42:53.72,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,It's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.58,0:42:58.59,Default,W,0,0,0,,If I stay with him, I'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.58,0:43:06.19,Bengoshi-Next_Episode,Caption,0,0,0,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.59,0:43:00.29,Default,M,0,0,0,,You can't even keep house properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.29,0:43:03.39,Default,M,0,0,0,,You're the one who left me! \NI won't give you a penny!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.39,0:43:06.19,Bengoshi-Top,Hakamada,0,0,0,,I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.42,0:43:06.19,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Right,Caption,0,0,0,,Divorce at Middle Age,{\c&HAEADB2&} After Compounded Suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.42,0:43:06.19,Bengoshi-End_Splash_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,A Housewife's Scream of Agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.19,0:43:09.53,Bengoshi-Top,W,0,0,0,,I can finally divorce my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.23,0:43:09.56,Bengoshi-Fiction,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,0)}This drama is a work of fiction.

